<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>TREMENDVZ - Heavy Metal Brasil</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel+Decorative:wght@700&family=Cinzel:wght@400;700;900&family=Raleway:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/index.css">
</head>
<body>

  <nav>
    <div class="nav-logo">TREMENDVZ</div>
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="#release">Álbum</a></li>
      <li><a href="#music">Músicas</a></li>
      <li><a href="#about">Banda</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg"></div>
    <canvas id="sparks"></canvas>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <p class="band-eyebrow">Heavy Metal ✦ Brasil</p>
      <h1 class="band-name">TREMENDVZ</h1>
      <p class="band-subtitle">Não sou conduzido, conduzo</p>
      <div class="hero-divider"></div>
      <div class="hero-cta">
        <button class="btn-primary" onclick="document.getElementById('release').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">Último Lançamento</button>
        <button class="btn-secondary" onclick="document.getElementById('music').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">Discografia</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="release">
    <div class="release-section">
      <div class="release-grid">
        <div class="album-art-wrap">
          <div class="album-art">
            <div class="album-art-inner">
              <div class="album-art-symbol">⚔</div>
              <div class="album-art-title">GLÓRIA E SANGUE</div>
              <div class="album-art-subtitle">TREMENDVZ · 2025</div>
            </div>
            <div class="album-badge">Novo Álbum</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="release-info">
          <div>
            <p class="section-label">Último Lançamento</p>
            <h2 class="section-title">Glória e Sangue</h2>
            <div class="gold-line"></div>
          </div>
          
          <div id="now-playing" class="active-track-banner">
            <div class="pulse"></div>
            <span class="active-track-title" id="now-playing-title"></span>
          </div>

          <ul class="tracklist" id="tracklist">
            <li class="track" data-track="Torture, Perpetual Darkness and Pain" onclick="selectTrack(this)">
              <span class="track-num">I</span>
              <span class="track-name">Torture, Perpetual Darkness and Pain</span>
              <div class="track-play">▶</div>
              <div class="track-bar"></div>
            </li>
            <li class="track" data-track="Before The Atrocious Power Of My Sword" onclick="selectTrack(this)">
              <span class="track-num">II</span>
              <span class="track-name">Before The Atrocious Power Of My Sword</span>
              <div class="track-play">▶</div>
              <div class="track-bar"></div>
            </li>
            <li class="track" data-track="NON DVCOR DVCO" onclick="selectTrack(this)">
              <span class="track-num">III</span>
              <span class="track-name">NON DVCOR DVCO</span>
              <div class="track-play">▶</div>
              <div class="track-bar"></div>
            </li>
            <li class="track" data-track="Weeping and Gnashing of Teeth" onclick="selectTrack(this)">
              <span class="track-num">IV</span>
              <span class="track-name">Weeping and Gnashing of Teeth</span>
              <div class="track-play">▶</div>
              <div class="track-bar"></div>
            </li>
            <li class="track" data-track="Glória e Sangue" onclick="selectTrack(this)">
              <span class="track-num">V</span>
              <span class="track-name">Glória e Sangue</span>
              <div class="track-play">▶</div>
              <div class="track-bar"></div>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <div class="streaming-links">
            <div class="stream-btn">Spotify</div>
            <div class="stream-btn">YouTube Music</div>
            <div class="stream-btn">Apple Music</div>
            <div class="stream-btn">Deezer</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section about-section" id="about">
    <div class="about-inner">
      <p class="section-label" style="text-align:center">A Banda</p>
      <p class="about-quote">"<em>Non Dvcor, Dvco.</em><br>Não sou conduzido — conduzo."</p>
      <div class="gold-line" style="margin:0 auto 2rem"></div>
      <p class="about-body">TREMENDVZ é uma banda brasileira de heavy metal que forja um som épico e visceral, ancorado em líricas de guerra, honra e intensidade humana. Composições de Luiz Gustavo Tavares, as músicas transitam entre o latim clássico e o inglês, invocando a tradição dos guerreiros imortais — aqueles que não são conduzidos, mas que conduzem.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="music">
    <div class="songs-section">
      <p class="section-label">Discografia</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Todas as Músicas</h2>
      <div class="gold-line"></div>
      
      <div class="songs-grid">
        <div class="song-card" onclick="alert('Buscando informações sobre: Torture, Perpetual Darkness and Pain')">
          <div class="song-card-num">01</div>
          <div class="song-card-title">Torture, Perpetual Darkness and Pain</div>
          <div class="song-card-subtitle">Faixa 1 · Álbum Glória e Sangue</div>
          <div class="song-card-icon">↗</div>
        </div>
        <div class="song-card" onclick="alert('Buscando informações sobre: Before The Atrocious Power Of My Sword')">
          <div class="song-card-num">02</div>
          <div class="song-card-title">Before The Atrocious Power Of My Sword</div>
          <div class="song-card-subtitle">Faixa 2 · Álbum Glória e Sangue</div>
          <div class="song-card-icon">↗</div>
        </div>
        <div class="song-card" onclick="alert('Buscando informações sobre: NON DVCOR DVCO')">
          <div class="song-card-num">03</div>
          <div class="song-card-title">NON DVCOR DVCO</div>
          <div class="song-card-subtitle">Não sou conduzido, conduzo</div>
          <div class="song-card-icon">↗</div>
        </div>
        <div class="song-card" onclick="alert('Buscando informações sobre: Weeping and Gnashing of Teeth')">
          <div class="song-card-num">04</div>
          <div class="song-card-title">Weeping and Gnashing of Teeth</div>
          <div class="song-card-subtitle">Faixa 4 · Álbum Glória e Sangue</div>
          <div class="song-card-icon">↗</div>
        </div>
        <div class="song-card" onclick="alert('Buscando informações sobre: Glória e Sangue')">
          <div class="song-card-num">05</div>
          <div class="song-card-title">Glória e Sangue</div>
          <div class="song-card-subtitle">Faixa Principal · Álbum Glória e Sangue</div>
          <div class="song-card-icon">↗</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <div class="footer-logo">TREMENDVZ</div>
    <p class="footer-tagline">Non Dvcor, Dvco · Heavy Metal · Brasil</p>
    <div class="footer-social">
      <span class="social-link">Instagram</span>
      <span class="social-link">YouTube</span>
      <span class="social-link">Spotify</span>
      <span class="social-link">Letras.mus.br</span>
    </div>
    <p class="footer-copy">© 2025 TREMENDVZ · Luiz Gustavo Tavares · Todos os direitos reservados</p>
  </footer>

  <script src="/js/index.js"></script>
</body>
</html>

